## Maintenance Checklist
- [ ] New mandatory policy is added to a rule file first.
- [ ] Skills reference rule anchors and avoid duplicating hard prohibitions.
- [ ] New skills include only procedural content and practical checklists.
- [ ] Conflicting language is removed immediately when discovered.
